===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fr}} {{term|myriade|lang=fr}}, from {{etyl|LL.}} {{term|myrias|lang=la}} (genitive of {{term|myriadis|lang=la}}), from {{etyl|grc}} {{term|μυριάδος|sc=polytonic|tr=myriados|lang=grc}}, genitive of {{term|μυριάς|sc=polytonic|tr=myrias||number of 10,000|lang=grc}}, from {{term|μύριος|sc=polytonic|tr=myrios||numberless, countless, infinite|lang=grc}}.

